  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT308-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">varaiviṭaik kiḻattiyai vaṉcol colli vaṟpuṟuttiyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Encouraging HER, speaking strong words at the time of
          marriage. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT308">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> cōlai vāḻaic curinukum piṉaiya</l>
          <l> vaṇaṅkuṭai yaruntalai nīvaliṉ mataṉaḻintu</l>
          <l> mayaṅkutuya ruṟṟa maiyal vēḻa</l>
          <l> muyaṅkuyir maṭappiṭi yulaipuṟan taivara</l>
          <l> vāmiḻi cilampi ṉaritukaṇ paṭukku</l>
          <l> māmalai nāṭaṉ kēṇmai</l>
          <l> kāman taruvatōr kaitāḻn taṉṟē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Bringing only desire [now] it has lowered [its] hand ,</l>
          <l>the friendship of the man from the land of big mountains,</l>
          <l rend="indent">where the proud elephant bull rarely closes [his] eyes,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">on the mountain slope where the water is falling,</l>
          <l rend="indent8">beset by confusing misery</l>
          <l rend="indent2">after [his] rutting vigour has perished from a curved leaf</l>
          <l rend="indent8">of the banana tree</l>
          <l rend="indent3">in the woods stroking [his] desperately tormented, difficult head,</l>
          <l rend="indent4">while the youthful female with weakened breath </l>
          <l rend="indent8">rubs [his] ruined back.</l>

          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="6+7b" resp="#TVG">
            <l>The friendship ... resulted in the singular habit of inducing desire.</l>
          </lg>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
